{"title":"腊月望归","authors":["刘明恒"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":1,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月望归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘明恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花把腊月漂得洁白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒风把腊月摇得嘎嘎作响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月正忙忙碌碌地走向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被欢乐和吉祥绽破的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟尘全掸净了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣被全洗净了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针线活全做完了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，家家门前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮着盼归的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花盖不住山道口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子那盼归的脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒风堵不住屋檐下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女们那盼归的唠叨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木炭火熔不开火炉旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人们那盼归的焦虑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁家的男人回来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃一串女人芬芳的欢笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引一串旁人急切的询问"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有那个年轻的少妇（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}